snippet.textDisplay:
A long drive on an empty highway…
Memories of a loved one echo with every mile.
Then, a cold breeze gently brushes my ears and whispers,
“Hijr-e-yaara na sata bewaja…”
(Don’t let the pain of separation torment you without reason.)
